oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Parko Enterprises Job No. 36525
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1084) for an order placed for Parko Enterprises by X. B. Cosse for 1,000 tickets (white) and 1,000 tickets (green) for a performance by the New Christy Minstrels at the Fairgrounds Coliseum on February 26. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
